  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear the lamb shoulder until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes per side.",
    "Remove the lamb from the pot and set it aside.",
    "Add the onion to the pot and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the tomatoes, tomato ketchup, red wine, salt, and black pepper to the pot.",
    "Stir to combine and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Return the lamb to the pot and add the lemon juice.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer it to the oven.",
    "Braise the lamb for 2 1/2 hours, or until tender and falling apart.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and stir in the fresh oregano and bay leaves.",
    "Serve the lamb hot, garnished with fresh oregano and lemon wedges."
